Through this application, you can encrypt the privacy information files such as pictures and videos in your mobile phone. The encrypted files can only be viewed in a private space. The encrypted files cannot be seen outside the private space, which fully protects your personal privacy.

The private space supports two login modes: password and fingerprint. You can enter the password to log in on the login interface. You can also log in by verifying the fingerprint after clicking the fingerprint login button (you need to set the lock screen and enter the fingerprint information first).

The private space supports quick exit from the application. After the quick exit switch is enabled on the setup interface, press the Home button and the menu button to quickly exit the application. Please pay attention to the applications exit method to avoid personal privacy leakage!
When you forget your password, you can click "Forgot Password" on the verification interface to reset the password by verifying the secret question, so please remember your secret question!
Before uninstalling the software, be sure to decrypt the encrypted file, otherwise it will cause the loss of the private file, please keep in mind!
